    "individual_blog_r874gP": {
      "type": "individual-blog",
      "blocks": {
        "rich_text_9hwRAc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>Instagram Poses That Show Off Your Engagement Ring Naturally</h1>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "follow_us_ygY8aG": {
          "type": "follow_us",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Follow Us on"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ccxpK9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Your engagement ring photos deserve to be photographed in a way that feels natural, refined and effortless - just like the story of how you fell in love! Today’s couples are moving from overly polished photoshoots to clicking photographs that whisper a story without feeling posed. These are authentically yours! The most captivating engagement ring photos aren’t the ones that scream attention but the ones where the ring shines and reflects a beautiful moment. Whether you are preparing for your pre-wedding photoshoot or simply capturing personal memories, these engagement ring couple photos  elevate your ring as well as your love story. Each one of them are curated to look natural while capturing the beauty of your ring. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BxFmqg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Car Mirror Reflection",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Car Mirror Reflection</h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-car"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AynJ8F": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_4eeb2d8a-aaae-4327-a64d-c9f95bbd72f7.jpg",
            "text": "<p>There’s something timelessly romantic about memories created inside the car. Hands intertwined, music playing in the background, sunlight pouring in and smiles exchanged, while the world moves outside the window.<br/>To click the photo, park the car where there is soft, even sunlight. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_YCFMNY": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Car Mirror Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Harsh sunlight will create a glare on the mirror. Hold your hand, showing off your ring. Flip open the sun visor mirror and angle it to focus on your hands held together, metaphorically - for the rest of your lives as your journey goes forward. </p><p>The reflection naturally puts the ring into the spotlight. This engagement ring hand photo feels personal, cinematic and beautiful. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jbd43L": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Lift & Laugh Moment the-lift ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Lift & Laugh Moment the-lift </h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-lift"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zpxzBh": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3_1_86e6482c-4da1-4d3d-85ba-07e0041b6ee2.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A lifted pose captures pure joy and motion. It is one of the very few engagement ring ceremony poses that reveals the ring beautifully in a candid way. In this picture, the groom lifts the bride from behind, making the bride lean forward towards the camera. Her face is lit up with a wide grin as she flaunts her ring. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_PYNpgj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Lift & Laugh Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>This hand pic with a ring blends emotion with elegance, allowing the ring to shine as part of a joyful story rather than the focal point.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ejh96n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Fiction And You - An Intimate And Editorial Pose",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Fiction And You - An Intimate And Editorial Pose</h2>",
            "custom_id": "fiction"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_VWDmRU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4_1c5c2735-0846-4fad-b11a-1918b360536b.jpg",
            "text": "<p>She reads novels. She tells you the plot. It is a ritual, right? This pose captures a relaxed moment while letting the ring appear organically.</p><p>Create this picture by positioning yourselves in front of each other by the window. Use the window’s soft lighting pouring inside and click a photo of the bride reading/flipping the page, while the fiance looks at her admiringly. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BWVmEe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Fiction And You  Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The groom can go an extra mile to add a layer of detail - by wearing her scrunchie on his wrist. </p><p>The result is refined, warm, homely and perfect for couples who appreciate understated luxury. Feel free to change the setting by clicking this picture in a garden or a bookstore. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bPLMNC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Suitcase Shot    ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Suitcase Shot    </h2>",
            "custom_id": "  the-suitcase"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zwVAkV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5_bc3071d3-6f47-4612-982f-1764329bedca.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Travel inspired shots are exactly what youngsters are looking for as they suggest a beginning to a journey forward - one filled with adventure and partnership. To set up the positioning, bring two suitcases side by side. Both partners rest one hand naturally on the suitcase handles, rings facing outward but not forced.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_TbC4mN": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Suitcase Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The frame now looks rich, modern and fun! Keep backgrounds simple with airport elements. This pose is perfect for editorial-style travel photography. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dEkM3m": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Rain-Kissed Moment   ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Rain-Kissed Moment </h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-rain"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NwRy9R": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/6_fa23b6a8-0c9e-44e9-b389-07d401e75011.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A teardrop shaped diamond encircled by a halo of smaller stones. This ring elongates the finger and sparkles from every angle, blending vintage charm with modern brilliance.</p><p>Say yes if you love designs that are soft yet striking. This modern engagement ring bridges classic romance with contemporary charm.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jMYfry": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Solitaire Heart Shape Diamond Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Solitaire Heart Shape Diamond Engagement Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": "solitaire"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iiFrKE": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7_8912f9a5-5de4-4b6e-92bc-9f662ef18fcb.jpg",
            "text": "<p>The <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-heart\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"heart shaped\">heart shaped</a> diamond engagement ring is the ultimate symbol of love, playful yet deeply personal. A piece that stands out in both meaning and shape. It's perfect for someone sentimental, who believes love should be felt and shown.</p><p>Say yes if your love story deserves a symbol as expressive as your heart.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CbXLkg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Emerald and Round Diamond Toi Et Moi Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Emerald and Round Diamond Toi Et Moi Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": "emerald"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NiGrXL": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/8_0f175032-32be-4047-94c3-0033e77bf139.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Our modern Toi et Moi pairs emerald and round cuts to create a design full of motion and symmetry. The two stones face each other, representing equality and partnership. This modern engagement ring feels modern but classic, a refreshing option for contemporary couples.<br/>Say yes if your relationship is built on balance and mutual admiration. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_hEAXhx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Pear Diamond Trilogy Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Pear Diamond Trilogy Engagement Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": "pear-diamond"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NN3FF4": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/9_41337834-d136-49b2-87aa-95316df739e4.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Three <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-pear\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pear shaped\">pear shaped</a> diamonds come together to create a design that's soft and dynamic. It is modern yet sentimental, and its fluid shape adds movement to sparkle. It is a beautiful option for someone who believes love keeps growing through every stage and season. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cTfgNx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Pear Diamond Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Say yes if you’re drawn to rare ring designs that carry deeper meaning and stand out  with sophistication.</p>",
            "custom_id": "hexa"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BfYxxj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Round Solitaire With Diamond Accented Split Shank Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Round Solitaire With Diamond Accented Split Shank Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": "round-solitaire"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_WhjVYq": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/10_262d448f-da8f-455a-95e4-b0ef5bfcb7fb.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A delicate twist on a classic, the split shank design adds depth and balance while keeping the silhouette clean. The side detailing catches light beautifully like a small touch to its character. Its elegant enough for everyday wear yet special enough for a lifetime.</p><p>Say yes if you love intricate designs that symbolise how your meant-to-be story unfolded over time. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jGPUrV": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": " Princess Cut Solitaire Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2> Princess Cut Solitaire Engagement Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": "princess"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_7bhRtt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/11.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Geometric, sharp, and endlessly radiant, this princess cut is the modern bride’s statement. It’s edges sparkle with precision, giving it a sleek, architectural appeal.</p><p>It’s perfect for those who love clarity and confidence in design <br/>Say yes if you want a ring that feels powerful yet feminine, a ring that moves with poise in every gesture.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ND9GCy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lab Grown Diamond Rings: A Modern Revolution",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lab Grown Diamond Rings: A Modern Revolution</h2><p>Every generation redefines what love and luxury mean. For today’s couples, its no longer just about sparkle, its about significance and that's where lab grown diamonds change the story. They offer the same beauty, brilliance and durability as mined diamonds but with a smaller environmental footprint.</p><p>They make it possible to invest in higher clarity or larger carat, all while choosing sustainably. </p><p>Say yes to diamonds that shine not only brighter, but truer, inside and out.</p>",
            "custom_id": "lab-grown"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cPbJNJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Custom Designs",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Custom Designs</h2><p>When love doesn't fit a mold, neither should your ring. That's why Lucira’s bespoke design experience begins with your story. Every detail, from the curve of the band to the way light hits your diamond, becomes a reflection of you. Maybe it's a hidden engraving that only you two know about. Maybe it's a diamond color inspired by the first city you travelled to together, a soft curve that mirrors the bridge of Paris or warm gold tone that reminds you of sunsets of Santorini. Or maybe its a design that feels nothing like what you’ve seen before because love in your world looks a little different.</p><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, our artisans turn emotions into form, sketch by sketch, setting by setting. Because the most meaningful rings are not just worn, they’re lived in.</p><p>So if your love deserves something that feels deeply, unmistakably yours, create with us.</p>",
            "custom_id": "custom"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3fBN74": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion - The Final Lucira Tip",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion: Your Yes, Your forever </h2><p>Choosing an engagement ring is both emotional and practical, a mix of instinct and intention. The right one won't just look beautiful; it will feel like home.</p><p>Whether it's the confidence of the radiant solitaire, the modern geometry of the princess cut or the tenderness of the heart shaped ring, each piece in Lucira Jewelry’s collection is designed to capture one thing, that perfect unforgettable yes.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
      },
